# cbpi4-DependentDelayActor

CraftBeerPi4 actor plugin.

It switches a selected target actor only after a selected dependency actor is in the required ON/OFF state. If enabled, the dependency actor is switched automatically first. An optional delay in seconds can be configured before the target actor is switched on.
